incident_updates.body: We are continuing to work on a fix for this issue.

Most of servers are now operational.
If you still experience an issue, don't hesitate to contact the support.

If you still experience an issue, don't hesitate to contact the support.
We are continuing to work on a fix for this issue.
Power will be restored on the impacted room early in the afternoon. An update will be published at 13:00 UTC
We will get back to you early this afternoon as soon as we have more information on this subject.
The issue has been identified and a fix is being implemented.
